contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_DateDtoFts_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `DateDto` BEGIN DELETE FROM `DateDtoFts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_DateDtoFts_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `DateDto` BEGIN DELETE FROM `DateDtoFts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_DateDtoFts_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `DateDto` BEGIN INSERT INTO `DateDtoFts`(`docid`, `dateHeading`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`dateHeading`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_DateDtoFts_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `DateDto` BEGIN INSERT INTO `DateDtoFts`(`docid`, `dateHeading`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`dateHeading`); END
